#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kcalc; is a calculator for your desktop environment. In the simple mode it "
"can be used for basic arithmetic operations, but provides advanced modes for "
"scientific, statistical and numeral system calculations."
msgstr ""
"&kcalc; est une calculatrice pour votre bureau. En mode simple, elle peut "
"être utilisée pour les opérations d'arithmétique basiques, mais elle possède "
"également un mode avancé pour les calculs scientifiques, statistiques et des "
"conversions de bases."

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keyword>KDE</keyword>"
msgstr "<keyword>KDE</keyword>"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid "KCalc"
msgstr "KCalc"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid "calculator"
msgstr "calculatrice"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Introduction"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kcalc; offers many more mathematical functions than meets the eye at a "
"first glance. Please study the section on keyboard accelerators and modes in "
"this handbook to learn more about the many functions available."
msgstr ""
"&kcalc; offre bien plus de fonctions mathématiques que l'on ne soupçonne au "
"premier abord. Veuillez regarder la section de ce manuel sur les raccourcis "
"clavier et les modes pour obtenir plus d'informations sur les nombreuses "
"fonctions disponibles."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In addition to the usual functionality offered by most scientific "
"calculators, &kcalc; offers a number of features, which I think are "
"worthwhile pointing out:"
msgstr ""
"En plus des nombreuses fonctionnalités offertes par la plupart des "
"calculatrices scientifiques, &kcalc; présente un certain nombre de "
"caractéristiques qui valent sans doute la peine d'être mentionnées :"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kcalc; provides trigonometric functions, logic operations, and it is able "
"to do statistical calculations."
msgstr ""
"&kcalc; fournit des fonctions trigonométriques, des opérations logiques et "
"il est capable de faire des calculs statistiques."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kcalc; allows you to cut and paste numbers from/into its display."
msgstr ""
"&kcalc; vous permet de copier / coller des nombres vers / depuis son "
"affichage."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kcalc; features a <firstterm>results-stack</firstterm> which lets you "
"conveniently recall previous results."
msgstr ""
"&kcalc; gère une <firstterm>pile de résultats</firstterm> qui vous permet de "
"rappeler commodément des résultats antérieurs."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can configure &kcalc;'s display colors and font."
msgstr ""
"Vous pouvez configurer les couleurs et la police d'affichage de &kcalc;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can configure &kcalc;'s precision, the number of displayed digits and "
"the number of digits after the period in the settings dialog."
msgstr ""
"Vous pouvez configurer la précision de &kcalc;, le nombre de chiffres "
"affichés ainsi que le nombre de chiffres après la virgule dans la fenêtre de "
"configuration."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kcalc; offers a great number of useful <link linkend=\"key-accels\"> key-"
"bindings</link>, which make using &kcalc; without using a pointing device "
"easy."
msgstr ""
"&kcalc; offre un grand nombre de <link linkend=\"key-accels\">raccourcis "
"clavier</link> pratiques qui rendent l'utilisation de &kcalc; sans "
"périphérique de pointage facile."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Hint: pressing (and holding) the &Ctrl;-key, displays on every button,the "
"corresponding key-binding."
msgstr ""
"Astuce : en pressant (et maintenant) la touche <keycap>&Ctrl;</keycap>, "
"apparait sur chaque bouton, le raccourci clavier correspondant."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kcalc; uses <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"Calculator_input_methods#Infix_notation\">Infix notation</ulink> which "
"enforces correct order of operations as taught in school; contrary to <ulink "
"url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"Calculator_input_methods#Immediate_execution\">Immediate execution</ulink> "
"used by many simple calculators."
msgstr ""
"&kcalc; utilise la <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"Calculator_input_methods#Infix_notation\">notation Infix</ulink> qui force "
"l'ordre correct des opérations enseigné à l'école, contrairement à l'<ulink "
"url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"Calculator_input_methods#Immediate_execution\">exécution immédiate</ulink> "
"utilisée par beaucoup de calculettes."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid "Have fun with &kcalc;!"
msgstr "Nous vous souhaitons de profiter agréablement de &kcalc; !"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Bernd.Johannes.Wuebben;"
msgstr "&Bernd.Johannes.Wuebben;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid "Usage"
msgstr "Utilisation"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid "General Usage"
msgstr "Utilisation générale"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"General usage is straightforward and similar to the way most simple "
"scientific calculators operate, but take note of the following special "
"&kcalc; features:"
msgstr ""
"L'utilisation de base est très simple et semblable au mode de fonctionnement "
"de la plupart des calculatrices scientifiques. Mais, veuillez prendre en "
"compte les caractéristiques suivantes propres à &kcalc; :"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:116
#, no-c-format
msgid "Result Stack"
msgstr "Pile de résultats"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each time you &LMB; click on the <guibutton>=</guibutton> button or press "
"your keyboard's &Enter; or <keysym>=</keysym> keys, the display result is "
"written to &kcalc;'s result stack. You can navigate through the result stack "
"with your keyboard's <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></"
"keycombo> and <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; &Shift;<keycap>Z</keycap></"
"keycombo> keys."
msgstr ""
"Chaque fois que vous cliquez avec le &BGS; sur la touche <guibutton>=</"
"guibutton> ou que vous appuyez sur les touches &Enter; ou <keysym>=</keysym> "
"de votre clavier, le résultat affiché est stocké dans la pile de résultats "
"de &kcalc;. Vous pouvez parcourir la pile de résultats grâce aux touches "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo> et <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; &Maj;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid "Percent Function"
msgstr "Fonction de pourcentage"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The percent function works somewhat differently to that on most calculators. "
"However, once understood, its enhanced functionality proves quite useful. "
"See the section about the <link linkend=\"percent\">percent</link> function "
"for further details."
msgstr ""
"La fonction de pourcentage fonctionne relativement différemment de celle de "
"la plupart des calculatrices. Toutefois, une fois son fonctionnement "
"compris, ses fonctionnalités améliorées se révèlent plutôt utiles. Reportez-"
"vous à la section <link linkend=\"percent\">pourcentages</link> pour plus de "
"détails."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cut and Paste"
msgstr "Copier / coller"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pressing <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo> will "
"place the displayed number onto the clipboard."
msgstr ""
"Un appui sur <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo> "
"placera le nombre affiché dans le presse-papier."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pressing <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></keycombo> will "
"paste the clipboard content into the display if the content of the clipboard "
"is a valid floating point number."
msgstr ""
"Le fait d'appuyer sur <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></"
"keycombo> a pour effet de coller le contenu du presse-papiers dans "
"l'affichage, si le contenu du presse-papiers est un nombre en virgule "
"flottante valable."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is still possible to copy/paste by clicking on &kcalc;'s display, but "
"this may disappear in future versions."
msgstr ""
"Il est toujours possible de faire des copier / coller en cliquant sur "
"l'affichage de &kcalc;, mais cela devrait disparaitre dans les versions "
"futures."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:158
#, no-c-format
msgid "Advanced functions"
msgstr "Fonctions avancées"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:160
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you start &kcalc; for the first time, the calculator will only display "
"buttons for basic arithmetic computations."
msgstr ""
"Lors du premier démarrage de &kcalc;, la calculatrice affiche uniquement les "
"boutons pour les calculs arithmétiques de base."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Under the menu entry <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> it is possible to select a "
"mode for &kcalc;: it is possible to choose <link linkend=\"simple-mode"
"\">Simple</link> or <link linkend=\"science-mode\">Science</link> or <link "
"linkend=\"statistical-mode\">Statistic</link> or <link linkend=\"numeral-"
"system-mode\">Numeral System</link> mode. Please note, that these modes will "
"slightly change as &kcalc; evolves."
msgstr ""
"Dans le menu <guimenu>Configuration</guimenu>, il est possible de "
"sélectionner un mode pour &kcalc; : il est possible de choisir <link linkend="
"\"simple-mode\">Mode Simple</link> ou <link linkend=\"science-mode\">Mode "
"Scientifique</link> ou <link linkend=\"statistical-mode\">Mode Statistique</"
"link> ou <link linkend=\"numeral-system-mode\">Mode Système numérique</"
"link>. Notez s'il vous plaît que ces modes seront légèrement modifiés au fur "
"et à mesure que &kcalc; évolue."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid "Button Layout"
msgstr "Disposition des boutons"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To give easy access to all the functions in advanced modes in &kcalc;, many "
"keys have a second layout. Click on <guibutton>&Shift;</guibutton> or press "
"the shortcut <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>2</keycap></keycombo> "
"to make the second layout of the buttons visible."
msgstr ""
"Pour garantir un accès aisé à toutes les fonctions de &kcalc;, de nombreuses "
"touches ont une seconde fonction. Cliquez sur <guibutton>&Maj;</guibutton> "
"en haut à droite, ou utilisez le raccourci <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>2</keycap></keycombo> pour afficher ces boutons."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid "History"
msgstr "Historique"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The history area shows all the calculations done in &kcalc; for the active "
"session of &kcalc;. Click on <guibutton>AC</guibutton> or press the shortcut "
"<keycap>Del</keycap> to clear the content of the history. To activate or "
"deactivate it, use the item <guilabel>Show History</guilabel> in the menu "
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> of the menu bar, or press <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>H</keycap></keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"La zone d'historique affiche tous les calculs effectués dans &kcalc; dans la "
"session active. Veuillez cliquer sur <guibutton>AC</guibutton> ou appuyer "
"sur le raccourci <keycap>Del</keycap> pour effacer le contenu de "
"l'historique. Pour l'activer ou le désactiver, veuillez utiliser l'élément "
"<guilabel>Afficher l'historique</guilabel> dans le menu "
"<guimenu>Configuration</guimenu> de la barre de menus ou appuyer sur "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>H</keycap></keycombo>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:198
#, no-c-format
msgid "Simple Mode"
msgstr "Mode Simple "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This mode contains only those buttons and functions, which are essential "
"necessary for basic calculations."
msgstr ""
"Ce mode comporte seulement les boutons et fonctions nécessaires pour les "
"calculs basiques."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:200
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you just want to sum up all items on an invoice this mode may be your "
"choice."
msgstr ""
"Si vous désirez additionner toutes les entrées d'une facture, ce mode "
"devrait vous convenir à merveille."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:205
#, no-c-format
msgid "Science Mode"
msgstr "Mode Scientifique"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this mode the left column of buttons is allocated to trigonometric "
"functions:"
msgstr ""
"Dans ce mode, la colonne de gauche de boutons est allouée aux fonctions "
"trigonométriques :"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:212 index.docbook:256 index.docbook:317 index.docbook:375
#, no-c-format
msgid "Buttons"
msgstr "Boutons"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:213 index.docbook:257 index.docbook:318 index.docbook:376
#: index.docbook:510
#, no-c-format
msgid "Function"
msgstr "Fonction"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:216 index.docbook:516
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Hyp</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>Hyp</guibutton>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:217
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter Hyperbolic sub mode. Hyp Sin for example is the hyperbolic sine: sinh"
msgstr ""
"Fait passer dans le sous-mode hyperbolique. Par exemple, Hyp Sin est le "
"sinus hyperbolique : sinh"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:220 index.docbook:521
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Sin</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>sin</guibutton>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:221
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compute the sine"
msgstr "Calcule le sinus"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:223
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Shift; <guibutton>Sin</guibutton> or <guibutton>Asin</guibutton>"
msgstr "&Maj; <guibutton>sin</guibutton> ou <guibutton>asin</guibutton>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compute the inverse sine"
msgstr "Calcule la fonction arcsinus"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:226 index.docbook:525
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Cos</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>cos</guibutton>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:227
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compute the cosine"
msgstr "Calcule le cosinus"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Shift; <guibutton>Cos</guibutton> or <guibutton>Acos</guibutton>"
msgstr "&Maj; <guibutton>cos</guibutton> ou <guibutton>acos</guibutton>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:230
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compute the inverse cosine"
msgstr "Calcule la fonction arccosinus"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:232 index.docbook:529
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Tan</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>tan</guibutton>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compute the tangent"
msgstr "Calcule la tangente"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:235
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Shift; <guibutton>Tan</guibutton> or <guibutton>Atan</guibutton>"
msgstr "&Maj; <guibutton>tan</guibutton> ou <guibutton>atan</guibutton>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compute the inverse tangent"
msgstr "Calcule la fonction arctangente"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:238 index.docbook:537
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Log</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>Log</guibutton>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:239
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compute the Log base 10"
msgstr "Calcule le logarithme décimal"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Shift; <guibutton>Log</guibutton> or 10<superscript>x</superscript>"
msgstr "&Maj; <guibutton>log</guibutton> ou 10<superscript>x</superscript>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:242
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compute 10 to the power of x"
msgstr "Calcule 10 puissance x"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:244 index.docbook:533
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Ln</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>ln</guibutton>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compute the natural logarithm. That is the log to base e"
msgstr "Calcule le logarithme naturel, celui de base e"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:247
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Shift; <guibutton>Ln</guibutton> or e<superscript>x</superscript>"
msgstr "&Maj; <guibutton>ln</guibutton> ou e<superscript>x</superscript>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:248
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compute e (the base of the natural logarithm) to the power of x"
msgstr "Calcule e (base du logarithme naturel) à la puissance x"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:252
#, no-c-format
msgid "The second column has buttons for algebraic functions:"
msgstr ""
"La deuxième colonne possède des boutons pour les fonctions algébriques :"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:260 index.docbook:634
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Mod</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>Mod</guibutton>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:261
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compute the remainder in Euclidean division"
msgstr "Calcule le reste dans la division euclidienne"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:263
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>&Shift;</guibutton> <guibutton>Mod</guibutton> or "
"<guibutton>IntDiv</guibutton>"
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>&Maj;</guibutton> <guibutton>Mod</guibutton> ou "
"<guibutton>IntDiv</guibutton>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:264
#, no-c-format
msgid "Integer division (integer part of the quotient)"
msgstr "Division entière (partie entière du quotient)"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:266 index.docbook:594
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>1/x</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>1/x</guibutton>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:267
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compute the reciprocal for a number"
msgstr "Calcule l'inverse d'un nombre"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:269
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>&Shift;</guibutton> <guibutton>1/x</guibutton> or <guibutton>nCm</"
"guibutton>"
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>&Maj;</guibutton> <guibutton>1/x</guibutton> ou <guibutton>nCm</"
"guibutton>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:270
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Compute the number of distinct second-operand-element subsets of it that can "
"be formed for any set containing first operand elements (binomial "
"coefficient)"
msgstr ""
"Calcule la coefficient binomial (nombre de sous-ensembles de (second terme) "
"éléments dans un ensemble de (premier terme) éléments)."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:272 index.docbook:558
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>x!</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>x ! </guibutton>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:273
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Compute the product of all positive integers less than or equal to the "
"current integer operand (factorial)"
msgstr ""
"Calcul la factorielle (produit de tous les entiers positifs inférieurs ou "
"égaux à l'entier courant)"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:275
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>x²</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>x²</guibutton>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:276
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compute the square of x"
msgstr "Calcule le carré de x"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:278
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
